Welcome to MaculaOS!

MaculaOS is a lightweight Linux distribution optimized for Macula edge nodes.
Pre-installed with k3s and Macula Console for zero-touch deployment.

Documentation: https://github.com/macula-io/macula-os
Issues: https://github.com/macula-io/macula-os/issues

To pair with Macula Portal, visit http://macula.local in your browser
or scan the QR code displayed during first boot.

